7. **CardManager Edit/Delete** — Inline editing and deletion
8. **CardManager Drag Within Column** — Reordering cards
9. **CardManager Drag Between Columns** — Cross-column card moves
10. **Playwright E2E Tests** — 8+ test scenarios covering all MVP features
11. **Documentation Updates** — AGENTS.md and README.md

